snippet.title: Animal Shelter 2: Prologue - Release Date Set
snippet.description:
A free Prologue of Animal Shelter 2 is set to release on September 13, 2024 at 5:00 PM CET! 🥳 With CO-OP mode - play with your friends! 😻👇

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2887780/Animal_Shelter_2_Prologue/

The next BIG step in the development of Animal Shelter 2 will start next week! Don't miss out and add it to your Wishlist now!
